Every application for the right to import lodged in accordance with Regulation (EC) No 1143/98 shall be granted to the following extent:
(a) for importers covered by (a) in Article 2 (1) of Regulation (EC) No 1143/98, 33,9662 % of the quantities imported during the period 1 July 1996 to 30 June 1999;
(b) for importers covered by (b) in Article 2 (1) of Regulation (EC) No 1143/98, 1,699 % of the quantities applied for.
